definitions.definition: Fighting or disposed to fight; belligerent , warlike .
Aggressively supporting of an idea , group , political or social cause, etc.; adamant , combative .

main_definition: Fighting or disposed to fight; belligerent , warlike . [from 15th c.]
secondary_definitions: Aggressively supporting of an idea , group , political or social cause, etc.; adamant , combative . [from 17th c.]
